<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00">今天是<delay8 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />万圣节哦～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已经<delay8 />等这一天等得太久了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />连心脏都要跳得炸裂啦！
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要有糖果对不对～？<delay20 />还有那套服装对不对～？<delay20 />
还有还有<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯！<delay20 />我都准备好了！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />终于迎来<delay8 />万圣节当天啦～！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />肯定连<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鬼怪们也很期待这一天，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />会兴致勃勃地跑出来玩吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呃，<delay20 />讨厌～！<delay20 />这样多吓人呀～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望真的鬼怪们<delay20 />
不会来参加<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />我都等不及夜色降临了～！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家要一起<delay8 />在万圣节活动上玩得开心些，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />留下<delay8 />美好的回忆才行哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">马上就是<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />万圣节活动的时间了哦！<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不给糖，就捣蛋！<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唔，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道真的要说时能不能说好呀～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我专门为了今天准备的<delay8 />
特别的乔装服装，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />值得你期待哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />活动就快开始了，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你没有忘了什么东西吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在万圣节忘东西，<delay8 /><anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />后果可是很严重的哦！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />尤其<delay20 /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是<delay8 />糖·<delay8 />果！<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是没有它的话，<delay20 />你会被恶作剧的！<delay frames="90" />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你问我？<delay40 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已经在衣服口袋里<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 /><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没、<delay8 />没错，<delay20 />在口袋里放满了糖果！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay40 />
<colour id="4" />惨了～！<delay40 />这件衣服的口袋<delay20 />
竟然开了个大洞呀～～！<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，<delay8 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />刚才<delay20 />我在<tag a="110" b="33" /><delay8 />
看到了南瓜的家具！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说到南瓜的话，<delay8 />当然会想到万圣节对吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定是哪个<delay20 />热爱节日活动的人<delay8 />
装饰在那里的～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你不觉得<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="33" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />洋溢着一股万圣节的气氛吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这都归功于某个<delay8 />
把岛装点得很漂亮的人呀！<delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我超感谢的～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多亏了<tag a="110" b="33" />上<delay8 />
随处可见的南瓜家具，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />万圣节的氛围才能这么浓厚～！
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过也因为这个原因，<delay20 />
我期待活动当天的激动心情都抑制不住了，<delay8 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真伤脑筋呀～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我说我说，<delay20 />这座<tag a="110" b="32" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是变成了万圣节的世界呀？！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我完完全全感受到<delay8 />
摆放装饰的那个人<delay8 />
对万圣节<delay20 />迸发的热情～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其他<tag a="110" b="32" />上的小伙伴<delay8 />要是看到了<delay8 />
一定会吓一跳的吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />实在太有氛围了，<delay8 />好棒呀～！
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />好想快一点<delay8 />
在万圣节版的<tag a="110" b="33" />上<delay20 />
享受活动的乐趣呀～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>